          </p>
        </div>
        
        {/* Hero Image */}
        <div className="mt-16 aspect-[21/9] bg-arzir-gray-200 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden">
          <Image
            src="/images/about/hero/manufacturing-facility.svg"
